data.eml:eml: Notes on the Pselaphinae (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae) in Shanghai, China

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Yin, Zi-Wei, Jiang, Ri-Xin, Chen, Zhi-Bing (2017): Notes on the Pselaphinae (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae) in Shanghai, China. Zootaxa 4238 (3): 433-439, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4238.3.10
